		GetQuote = function(symbol) {
			if (symbol.trim() == '') {
				$("#ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_ucView_c_views_c_ucGQWidget_txtNameSymbol").focus();
			}
			else {
				//js: duplicated header search box url encoding functionality here
				//convert ampersand to the word "and" so the querystring doesn't get cut short when being decoded
				//-- also convert multiple dashes to a single dash, multiple asterisks to a single asterisk,
				//-- replace double quotes with single quotes, and continue with remaining url encoding
				symbol = symbol.replace(/[&]/g, "and");
				symbol = symbol.replace(/--+/g, "-");
				symbol = symbol.replace(/[*][*]+/g, "*");
				symbol = symbol.replace(/\x22/g, "'");
				symbol = symbol.replace(/[<>%\\\/\|]/g, "").trim();
				symbol = symbol.replace(/[\s]/g, "+");
				window.open('https://research.sharebuilder.com/sharebuilder/stocks/snapshot?symbol=' + symbol, '_self');
			}
		};

			});
